@page "/information"

<div class="header">
    <h3>Information</h3>
</div>
    <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card education-card">
            <h4>Education Program</h4>
            <p>Meow! Hello, lovely human! I'm here to purr-suade you to check out the SPCA's education program...</p>
            <button class="view-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/Userchat'">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card volunteers-card">
            <h4>Volunteers</h4>
            <p>The SPCA welcomes volunteers with open paws! They’re always looking for big-hearted humans...</p>
            <button class="view-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/Volunteer'">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card pbo-card">
            <h4>We are A PBO</h4>
            <p>Woof Woof hey there, did you know that the SPCA is a PBO (Public Benefit Organization)?...</p>
            <button class="view-btn">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card pet-boarding-card">
            <h4>Pet Boarding</h4>
            <p>🐾 Heyy Heyy! The SPCA offers fantastic pet boarding services. They ensure pets are safe and loved...</p>
            <button class="view-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/Boarding'">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card adoption-card">
            <h4>Adoption</h4>
            <p>Hi there! Woof woof! If you're thinking about adding a furry friend to your family, consider adopting...</p>
            <button class="view-btn">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card charity-shop-card">
            <h4>Charity Shop</h4>
            <p>The SPCA's charity store is stocked with pet goodies. Visit to find treats, toys, and more while supporting a cause...</p>
            <button class="view-btn">View</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card sponsors-card">
            <h4>Sponsors and Donations</h4>
            <p>The SPCA relies on donations to keep our tails wagging and purrs loud! Every bit of support counts...</p>
            <button class="view-btn">View</button>
        </div>
    </div>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #143963;
        color: white;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .scroll-container {
        max-height: calc(100vh - 60px);
        overflow-y: auto;
    }
    .card-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 15px;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .card {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
    }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            background-color: #143963;
            color: white;
        }

    /* Specific card colors */
    .education-card {
        background-color: #FBD1CF;
        color: #333;
    }

    .volunteers-card {
        background-color: #9EACA4;
        color: #333;
    }

    .pbo-card {
        background-color: #5FB372;
        color: #333;
    }

    .pet-boarding-card {
        background-color: #B290AB;
        color: #333;
    }

    .adoption-card {
        background-color: #FFDA77;
        color: #333;
    }

    .charity-shop-card {
        background-color: #C6E5F2;
        color: #333;
    }

    .sponsors-card {
        background-color: #E3A7B1;
        color: #333;
    }

    h4 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: inherit;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* View button */
    .view-btn {
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding: 8px 15px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #143963;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 1em;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        .view-btn:hover {
            background-color: #143963;
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

    /* View More button styling */
    .view-more-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .view-more-btn {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #143963;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-size: 1.2em;
        box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        .view-more-btn:hover {
            background-color: #FBD1CF;
            color: #143963;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
</style>
